%description
This is a package for Non-Negative Linear Models (NNLM). It implements
fast sequential coordinate descent algorithms for non-negative linear
regression and non-negative matrix factorization (NMF). It supports mean
square error and Kullback-Leibler divergence loss. Many other features are
also implemented, including missing value imputation, domain knowledge
integration, designable W and H matrices and multiple forms of
regularizations.

